 # New git repo {{apache/solr-mcp-server}}
 # Standalone app in monorepo, e.g. {{solr/mcp-server}}, much like prometheus-exporter used to be
 # Integrate as request handler in a new Solr module {{solr/modules/mcp}}

Benefit of 1 and 2 is more flexible deployment, exising code ready to go. Of course 3 would be nice but if it means 2 months of refactoring the contribution, then it may never happen?

